item.title: About
item.description: About Me Hey there! I am Salik, an 19 y.o, mostly known as P-Salik on social media platforms. I’m an android development (amateur), inspired from Sarthak Roy , Sakthivel Nadar, TechyMinati (Aryan Sinha) and Debayan Kar. I’ve worked for Realme C2 and I love android development. I mostly use github for my projects. Some of my works on github include: https://github.com/P-Salik/android_device_realme_RMX1941 https://github.com/P-Salik/android_vendor_realme_RMX1941 https://github.com/P-Salik/kernel_realme_RMX1941 I’m mostly active on Telegram. You can also reach me through Mail.
